title: The Krait - Trance Harmonics Radio 014 [17-04-14]
description:
The following is the podcast of DJ - The Krait's Trance Harmonics Radio Episode - 014 As Aired on 17-04-2014 on www. trancefamilybelgium. be/tfb-radio as well as www. thekrait. tk. 

The Show airs Every Thursday 4PM (CET Timing) During Winters and 5PM (CET) During Summers. You Can Also Download TFB-Radio App From Google Play Store.

If You Download This Show And Enjoy it, Do Give a Kudos on - www. facebook. com/thekrait and www. facebook. com/tranceharmonics
